reviews.text: Tried this new place in Sai Kung. I wanted to try the pie they offered. It was a big crispy pastry sandwich with beef and onion filling. Was a good size and very taste. My husband and daughter had the noodles and said they were very good. Well worth a visit.
It would be the greatest homemade noodles in sai kung
Good people, good food. I always order the spicy beef onion pie.
The things are good very spicy, if you want hot stuff for cold day, thats it, yet the service is bad, actually only one staff there, you needa wait awhile for them lol
Waitress is quite rude but food is great. I love the flat noodles here.

見到好多人食。但可能味道唔適合我，所以肚餓都食唔落
這次點了油麵當底、炸魚皮、白蘿蔔、燙生菜、豬腸，新鮮好吃，下次有機會再來吃，值得推薦 😀

dirty food, only outsider be there.

reviews.text: Tried this new place in Sai Kung. I wanted to try the pie they offered. It was a big crispy pastry sandwich with beef and onion filling. Was a good size and very taste. My husband and daughter had the noodles and said they were very good. Well worth a visit.
伴麵最好食，麵條可選，好有口感。湯都可以選。如果可以外買麵條就好了。店裡位置置比較少。

俾粗麵顯出功架呃左...
所以overpriced 都去試
麵好硬
胡椒湯好咸
豬軟骨更咸又鞋又多細碎骨
員工態度頗差
完全唔明有咩功架可言，食唔完個麵，因為好似食緊膠
唯一好係無味精
食物 ok, 但伙記態度一般！
其實見到好耐未試過因為每次都好多人今日有機會試下可以係好好食
